Alternatives of apache Tailer class
------------------------------------
	> https://github.com/davidmoten/rxjava-file
	> https://github.com/maartenl/jtail/tree/master/src/com/tools/jtail


Type of output 
---------------
	http
		> https support
		> number of retry OR none
		> path as Array
		> bulk_max_size
	
	kafka
		> number of retry OR none
		> path as Array
		> bulk_max_size
			
	redis
		> number of retry OR none
		> path as Array
		> bulk_max_size
			
	logstash
		> basic protocol 
